><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://pma2010.org/node/237\"><i>Defining Transformation for Social Change</i></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20100720200008/http://pma2010.org/node/237\">Archived</a> 2010-07-20 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>., 2010 <a href=\"/wiki/US_Social_Forum\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"US Social Forum\">US Social Forum</a> People's Movement Assembly, Detroit, MI \u2013 June 22\u201326, 2010</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://seasonsfund.org/?page_id=12\">Transformative Leadership Awards, 2009</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://seasonsfund.org/?page_id=16\">Seasons Fund website</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>Reading Freire and Habermas: Critical Pedagogy and Transformative Social Change</i>, Teachers College Press, 2002, <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-8077-4202-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-8077-4202-3\">0-8077-4202-3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Claudia Horwitz &amp; Jesse Maceo Vega-Frey (2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.berkana.org/articles/spiritual_activism.htm\"><i>Spiritual Activism and Liberation Spirituality: Pathways To Collective Liberation</i></a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cit